  "english": [
    "With regard to <b>anyone who deposits</b> an item with another, it is <b>with the awareness</b> that at times, the bailee’s <b>wife and his children</b> will safeguard the item that <b>he deposits</b> it. Therefore, I was within my rights to give the deposit to my mother.",
    "<b>Let us say to his mother: Go</b> and <b>pay.</b> She can <b>say:</b> My son <b>did not tell me that</b> the money <b>is not his</b> so <b>that I should bury it,</b> which is the optimal method to safeguard money.",
    "<b>Let us say to</b> the bailee: <b>Why did you not say to her</b> that the money is not yours? <b>He</b> can <b>say: All the more so</b> that my omission of this information was preferable, <b>as when I say to her that</b> the money <b>is mine, she is</b> even <b>more careful with it.</b>",
    "<b>Rather, Rava said:</b> The bailee <b>takes an oath that he gave</b> the money <b>to his mother, and his mother takes an oath that she placed the money in the chest and it was stolen, and</b> the bailee is <b>exempt</b> from payment.",
    "The Gemara relates: There was <b>a certain steward</b> who acted on behalf <b>of orphans, who purchased an ox for the orphans and passed it to the cowherd.</b> This ox <b>did not have molars and</b> other <b>teeth with which to eat, and</b> the ox <b>died</b> because it was unable to eat the standard food of oxen. <b>Rami bar Ḥama said: How should judges rule in this case?</b>",
    "<b>Let them say to the steward: Go pay</b> for the dead ox. But he can <b>say: I gave it to the cowherd</b> with the expectation that he would care for it.",
    "<b>Let us say to the cowherd: Go pay</b> for the dead ox. <b>He</b> can <b>say: I placed</b> the ox <b>with</b> other <b>oxen and I threw food before it. We did not know that it did not eat.</b>",
    "The Gemara asks: <b>After all, the cowherd is a paid bailee of the orphans.</b> Therefore, <b>he was required to examine</b> the situation and ascertain if the ox was eating. The Gemara answers: <b>If there was loss for the orphans, indeed,</b> the cowherd would be liable to pay. <b>And with what are we dealing here?</b> It is a case <b>where there is no loss</b> incurred <b>by the orphans, as they found the</b> previous <b>owner of the ox,</b> who sold it to them, <b>and the orphans took</b> their <b>money</b> back <b>from him</b> after discovering that the ox had this deficiency.",
    "The Gemara asks: <b>Rather, who</b> then <b>claims</b> compensation from the cowherd? <b>The</b> previous <b>owner of the ox claims</b> compensation from the steward: <b>He should have informed us</b> that the ox was not eating. The Gemara answers: <b>What</b> would <b>we inform</b> the previous owner? <b>He knows that it is a mistaken transaction,</b> as he would be aware that the ox had no teeth. The Gemara explains: This is a case <b>with regard to a trader who buys from here and sells to there</b> and does not know the condition of the ox. <b>Therefore,</b> the trader <b>takes an oath</b> that <b>he did not know</b> about the ox’s defect, <b>and the cowherd pays the value of the meat</b> of the ox <b>based on</b> the <b>cheapest</b> price available in the market.",
    "The Gemara relates: There was <b>a certain man who deposited hops,</b> used in the production of beer, <b>with another.</b> The bailee <b>himself had a pile of hops.</b> The bailee <b>said to his brewer: Cast</b> hops in the beer <b>from this</b> pile. The brewer <b>went and cast from</b> the <b>other</b> pile, the pile of the one who deposited the hops, into the beer. <b>Rav Amram said: How should judges rule in this case?</b>",
    "<b>Let us say to</b> the bailee: <b>Go pay.</b> But he can <b>say: I said to him,</b> i.e., the brewer: <b>Cast</b> hops <b>from this</b> pile, and I am not at fault.",
    "<b>Let us say to the brewer: Go pay.</b> He can <b>say:</b> The bailee <b>did not say to me: Cast</b> hops <b>from this</b> pile <b>and do not cast</b> hops <b>from that</b> pile. I thought he was merely giving advice, and I did not know that he was insistent that I refrain from using the other hops.",
    "The Gemara comments: <b>And</b> if the hops of the bailee were closer to where he and the brewer were located than those that were deposited with him, the bailee should be liable. As, <b>if</b> the brewer <b>delayed</b> bringing the hops for the <b>period</b> of time that it would take <b>to bring</b> the bailee hops from his own pile <b>and he did not</b> yet <b>bring them to him,</b> it is assumed that the bailee understood that the brewer had gone to bring the more distant, deposited, hops. By not objecting, the bailee <b>revealed that he was amenable</b> to brewing the beer from the deposited hops. The Gemara answers: This is a case <b>where he did not delay</b> bringing the hops, or alternatively, the two piles were equidistant from him.",
    "The Gemara asks: <b>Ultimately, what loss is there? But doesn’t</b> the bailee <b>profit</b> in this case? Let the bailee give the owner beer equal to the value of the hops that he took from the deposit and no one loses. <b>Rav Sama, son of Rava, said:</b> The Gemara is referring to a case <b>where the beer</b> ferments and <b>becomes vinegar.</b> Therefore, it is impossible to take the value of the hops from the beer. <b>Rav Ashi said:</b> It is referring to a case where the hops were mixed <b>with thorns</b> and did not enhance the beer."
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>כׇּל הַמַּפְקִיד, עַל דַּעַת אִשְׁתּוֹ וּבָנָיו הוּא",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַפְקִיד. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>נֵימָא לַהּ לְאִימֵּיהּ: זִילִי שַׁלִּימִי, אָמְרָה:",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לָא אֲמַר לִי דְּלָאו דִּידֵיהּ נִינְהוּ דְּאֶקְבְּרִינְהוּ.",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>נֵימָא לֵיהּ: אַמַּאי לָא אֲמַרְתְּ לַהּ? אָמַר: כׇּל שֶׁכֵּן,",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּכִי אָמֵינָא לַהּ דְּדִידִי נִינְהוּ – טְפֵי מִזְדַּהֲרָא בְּהוּ.",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֶלָּא אָמַר רָבָא: מִשְׁתְּבַע אִיהוּ דְּהָנְהוּ זוּזֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אַשְׁלְמִינְהוּ לְאִימֵּיהּ, וּמִשְׁתַּבְעָא אִימֵּיהּ דְּהָנְהוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "זוּזֵי אוֹתְבִינְהוּ בְּקַרְטְלִיתָא וְאִיגְּנוּב – וּפָטוּר. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>הָהוּא",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אַפּוֹטְרוֹפָּא דְיַתְמֵי דִּזְבַן לְהוּ תּוֹרָא לְיַתְמֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וּמַסְרֵיהּ לְבַקָּרָא. לָא הֲווֹ לֵיהּ כַּכֵּי וְשִׁינֵּי",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְמֵיכַל, וּמִית. אָמַר רָמֵי בַּר חָמָא: הֵיכִי נְדַיְינוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דַּיָּינֵי לְהַאי דִּינָא? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>נֵימָא לֵיהּ לְאַפּוֹטְרוֹפָּא: זִיל",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שַׁלֵּים, אָמַר: אֲנָא לְבַקָּרָא מְסַרְתֵּיהּ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>נֵימָא לֵיהּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְבַקָּרָא: זִיל שַׁלֵּים, אָמַר: אֲנָא בַּהֲדֵי תּוֹרֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹקֵימְתֵּיהּ, אוּכְלָא שְׁדַאי לֵיהּ, לָא הֲוָה יָדַעְינָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּלָא אֲכַל. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>מִכְּדֵי בַּקָּרָא שׁוֹמֵר שָׂכָר דְּיַתְמֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הוּא! אִיבְּעִי לֵיהּ לְעַיּוֹנֵי אִי אִיכָּא פְּסֵידָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְיַתְמֵי. הָכִי נָמֵי, וְהָכָא בְּמַאי עָסְקִינַן – דְּלֵיכָּא",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "פְּסֵידָא דְיַתְמֵי, דְּאַשְׁכְּחוּהּ לְמָרֵיהּ דְּתוֹרָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וּשְׁקוּל יַתְמֵי זוּזֵי מִינֵּיהּ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"8\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֶלָּא מַאן קָא טָעֵין?",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מָרֵיהּ דְּתוֹרָא קָטָעֵין. אִיבְּעִי לֵיהּ לְאוֹדוֹעַן! מַאי",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מוֹדְעִינַן לֵיהּ? מִידָּע יָדַע דְּמִקָּח טָעוּת הָוֵי.",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּסַפְסֵירָא דְּזָבֵן מֵהָכָא וּמְזַבֵּין לְהָכָא, הִלְכָּךְ",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִישְׁתְּבַע אִיהוּ דְּלָא הֲוָה יָדַע, וּמְשַׁלֵּם בַּקָּרָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּמֵי בָשָׂר בְּזוֹל. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"9\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>הָהוּא גַּבְרָא דְּאַפְקֵיד",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כְּשׁוּתָא גַּבֵּי חַבְרֵיהּ, הֲוָה לֵיהּ לְדִידֵיהּ נָמֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כַּרְיָא דִכְשׁוּתָא. אֲמַר לֵיהּ לְסַרְסְיֵהּ: מֵהַאי רְמֵי. אֲזַל",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "רְמָא מֵאִידַּךְ. אָמַר רַב עַמְרָם: הֵיכִי נְדַיְינוּ דַּיָּינֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְהַאי דִּינָא? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"10\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>נֵימָא לֵיהּ לְדִידֵיהּ: זִיל שַׁלֵּים, אָמַר:",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֲנָא אָמְרִי לֵיהּ מֵהַאי רְמִי. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"11\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>נֵימָא לֵיהּ לְסַרְסְיֵהּ:",
      "segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "זִיל שַׁלֵּים, אָמַר: לָא אֲמַר לִי מֵהַאי רְמִי וּמֵהַאי לָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "תִּרְמֵי. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"12\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְאִי דִּשְׁהָא שִׁיעוּר לְאֵיתוֹיֵי לֵיהּ וְלָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        12
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אַיְיתִי לֵיהּ – גַּלִּי אַדַּעְתֵּיהּ דְּנִיחָא לֵיהּ! בִּדְלָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        12
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁהָא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"13\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>סוֹף סוֹף, מַאי פְּסֵידָא אִיכָּא? וְהָא קָא",
      "segment_ids": [
        13
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִשְׁתָּרְשִׁי לֵיהּ! אָמַר רַב סַמָּא בְּרֵיהּ דְּרָבָא:",
      "segment_ids": [
        13
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דַּהֲוָה שִׁיכְרָא חַלָּא. רַב אָשֵׁי אָמַר: בְּכִיסֵי,",
      "segment_ids": [
        13
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>כׇּל הַמַּפְקִיד.</b> על דעת שלא יהא שומר נמנע מלמוסרן לאנשי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ביתו הגדולים ונאמנים לו הוא דמפקיד: <b>נימא</b> <b>לה</b> <b>לאימיה.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שתשלם בשביל שלא קברתו: <b>לבקרא</b> <b>מסרתיה.</b> היה לו להודיעני",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שאינו אוכל: <b>איבעי</b> <b>ליה</b> <b>לעיוני.</b> אם אוכל אם לאו: <b>אי</b> <b>איכא</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>פסידא</b> <b>ליתמי</b> <b>כו'.</b> תירוצא הוא:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>דְּאַשְׁכְּחוּהּ לְמָרֵיהּ דְּתוֹרָא</b> המוכר:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:8:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>וּשְׁקוּל.</b> דאמרי ליה מקח טעות",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:8:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הוא: <b>אלא</b> <b>מאן</b> <b>טעין.</b> מי תובע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:8:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כלום דקאמר (רבא) היכי נידיינו:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:8:4",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>מָרֵיהּ דְּתוֹרָא קָטָעֵין.</b> ושואל שמתה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בהמתו אצלך ותובע את האפוטרופוס:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>בְּסַפְסֵירָא.</b> קונה ומוכר בהמות בשוק",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ביום שקנה מוכר: <b>משתבע</b> <b>ספסירא.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דלא הוה ידע: <b>ומשלם</b> <b>בקרא</b> <b>דמי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>בשר</b> <b>בזול.</b> ותמיה אני מנין לרמי בר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "חמא דין זה מה לו לספסירא עם",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הרועה לא שומר שלו הוא ונראה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לי דמתניתין (<a href=\"/bava_metzia/35b\">לעיל בבא מציעא דף לה:</a>) דהשוכר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הפרה לחבירו והשאילה לאחר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ומתה כדרכה דקאמר ר' יוסי יחזיר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "פרה לבעלים ואוקימנא הלכה כר'",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "יוסי אלמא אע\"פ שאין הבעלים בעלי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דברים של שואל והשוכר שהוא לו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בעל דברים אינו חסר כלום שהרי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "פטור באונסין אפי' הכי הואיל ויש",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לו דין על השואל לגבות יעמדו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הבעלים הראשונים במקומן וגובין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מן השואל ה\"נ הואיל ויש ליתומים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לגבות מן הרועה שהוא שומר שכר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שלהם יעמדו בעלים במקום היתומים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "וגובין ומיהו אי הוה מפסדי יתומים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לא היה עושה פשרה בממון יתומים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לשלם בזול דיתמי לאו בני מחילה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "נינהו אבל עכשיו שהוא מגבה לבעלים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "וכאן אין פשיעה כל כך דאמר בהדי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "תוראי אוקימתיה כו' הטיל פשרה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ביניהם ולא ישלם כל דמי השור כמות",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שהוא חי אלא העור יחזיר לבעלים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "והבשר שמין וישלם שני שלישים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דהיכא דאמרינן בגמרא משלם בזול",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כל זוזא שהוא שש מעה כסף חשבינן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בארבעה דנקי בפרק מי שמת (ב\"ב",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דף קמו:): <b>כשותא.</b> הומלו\"ן שמטילין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לתוך השכר: <b>כריא.</b> כרי: <b>אמר</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>ליה.</b> בעל הבית: <b>לסרסיה.</b> לאשר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "על ביתו העושה שכר שלו: <b>מהא</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>רמי.</b> הראהו הכרי שלו וא\"ל מזה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "תטיל לשכר: <b>מאידך.</b> של פקדון: <b>ואי</b> <b>דשהא</b> <b>שיעור</b> <b>כו'.</b> גמ' פריך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אם היה כרי שלו קרוב ושל פקדון רחוק ושהא השליח שיעור מהלך דרך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הקרוב ולא אייתי: <b>גלי</b> <b>דעתיה.</b> דבעל הבית דניחא ליה שהרי ידע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שמשל פקדון הוי ולא מיחה בידו: <b>והא</b> <b>קמשתרשי</b> <b>ליה.</b> והלא הוא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "נשכר הכשות של פקדון שהטילו בשכר ושלו עומד וישלם משלו:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Bava Metzia 42b:9:3",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>חלא.</b> החמיץ: <b>בכיסי.</b> שהיתה כישות גרועה וקוצים מעורבין"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בה דלא השביח השכר כרצונו וקשה בעיניו שהטילוהו בתוכו:"
    }
