      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וממתני' דהנזקין (גיטין דף",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Bava Metzia 42b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נב.) דקתני מינהו ב\"ד לא ישבע מינהו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Bava Metzia 42b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אבי יתומים ישבע אבא שאול אומר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Bava Metzia 42b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חילוף הדברים אין להוכיח דחייב",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Bava Metzia 42b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
